author: wn.com
title: Prosecutors can chase political misconduct without John Doe
text: MADISON, Wis. (AP) - A new Wisconsin law limiting secret John Doe probes doesn't mean prosecutors' days of pursuing political corruption are over. But their remaining tools have limitations that may make it more difficult, especially in complex cases, legal experts say. Prosecutors and investigators will have to turn to ... ...
